author: Sy Bean
title: Photos: Sounders tie the Galaxy, 1-1
text: Photos: Sounders tie the Galaxy, 1-1 Originally published October 4, 2015 at 8:56 pm Seattle’s Chad Barrett (19) scores a goal to tie the game in the last three minutes of the game on Sunday at CenturyLink Field. (Sy Bean / The Seattle Times) LA’s Leonardo (22) collides with Seattle’s Obafemi Martins in the first half. (Sy Bean / The Seattle Times) LA’s Steven Gerrard (8) and Robbie Rogers chase a ball after Seattle’s Andreas Ivanschitz (23) slide tackled the ball in the first half. (Sy Bean / The Seattle Times) Seattle’s Obafemi Martins (9) collides with LA’s Omar Gonzalez in the first half. (Sy Bean / The Seattle Times) LA’s Donovan Ricketts (1) boots a ball downfield before Seattle’s Lamar Neagle (27) can reach it in the first half. (Sy Bean / The Seattle Times) Seattle’s Lamar Neagle (27) battles for the ball with LA’s Leonardo (22) in the first half. (Sy Bean / The Seattle Times) Seattle’s Andreas Ivanschitz goes up for a header in the first half. (Sy Bean / The Seattle Times) LA’s Gyasi Zardes (11) and Seattle’s Zach Scott go up for a header int he first half. (Sy Bean / The Seattle Times) Seattle’s Clint Dempsey (2) goes flying after being hit by LA’s Omar Gonzalez (4) in the first half.
